msgid ""
"Refer to [supported "
"features](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md) to get the"
" model's supported feature matrix."
msgstr "请参阅[支持的特性矩阵](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md)获取模型支持的特性列表。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:15
