#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:17
msgid "3 Prerequisites"
msgstr "3.前提条件"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:19
msgid "3.1 Model Weight"
msgstr "3.1 模型权重"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:21
msgid ""
"`Kimi-K2-Thinking` (bfloat16): requires 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16) node. "
"[Download model "
"weight](https://huggingface.co/moonshotai/Kimi-K2-Thinking)."
msgstr ""
"`Kimi-K2-Thinking`（bfloat16）：需要 1 个 Atlas 800 A3（64G × "
"16）节点。[下载模型权重](https://huggingface.co/moonshotai/Kimi-K2-Thinking)。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:23
msgid ""
"It is recommended to download the model weight to the shared directory, "
"such as `/mnt/sfs_turbo/.cache/`."
msgstr "建议将模型权重下载到共享目录，例如 `/mnt/sfs_turbo/.cache/`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:25
msgid ""
"After downloading the model weights, please edit the value of "
"`\"quantization_config.config_groups.group_0.targets\"` from "
"`[\"Linear\"]` to `[\"MoE\"]` in `config.json` of the original model to "
"verify the quantized model."
msgstr ""
"下载模型权重后，请在原始模型的 `config.json` 中将 "
"`\"quantization_config.config_groups.group_0.targets\"` 的值从 "
"`[\"Linear\"]` 修改为 `[\"MoE\"]` 以验证量化模型。"

