msgid "4 Installation"
msgstr "4.安装"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:62
msgid "4.1 Docker Image Installation"
msgstr "4.1 Docker 镜像安装"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:64
msgid "You can use the official Docker image to run `Kimi-K2-Thinking` directly."
msgstr "您可以使用官方 Docker 镜像直接运行 `Kimi-K2-Thinking`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:66
msgid ""
"Select an image based on your machine type and start the Docker image on "
"your node, refer to [using docker](../../installation.md#set-up-using-"
"docker)."
msgstr ""
"根据您的机器类型选择镜像，并在节点上启动 Docker 镜像，请参考[使用 Docker 安装](../../installation.md"
"#set-up-using-docker)。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:108
msgid "**Parameter Descriptions:**"
msgstr "**参数说明：**"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:110
msgid ""
"`IMAGE`: specifies the `vllm-ascend` image. The `-a3` suffix selects the "
"Atlas A3 image."
msgstr "`IMAGE`：指定 `vllm-ascend` 镜像。`-a3` 后缀选择 Atlas A3 镜像。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:111
msgid "`NAME`: specifies the container name."
msgstr "`NAME`：指定容器名称。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:112
msgid ""
"`--net=host`: uses host networking, so the vLLM service port is exposed "
"on the host directly."
msgstr "`--net=host`：使用主机网络，vLLM 服务端口直接暴露在主机上。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:113
msgid "`--shm-size=1g`: configures container shared memory."
msgstr "`--shm-size=1g`：配置容器共享内存。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:114
msgid ""
"`--device /dev/davinci[0-15]`: exposes 16 Ascend NPU devices to the "
"container."
msgstr "`--device /dev/davinci[0-15]`：向容器暴露 16 个 Ascend NPU 设备。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:115
msgid ""
"`--device /dev/davinci_manager`, `--device /dev/devmm_svm`, and `--device"
" /dev/hisi_hdc`: expose required Ascend runtime device files."
msgstr "`--device /dev/davinci_manager`、`--device /dev/devmm_svm` 和 `--device /dev/hisi_hdc`：暴露所需的 Ascend 运行时设备文件。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:116
msgid ""
"`-v /usr/local/dcmi:/usr/local/dcmi`: mounts DCMI tools for device "
"management."
msgstr "`-v /usr/local/dcmi:/usr/local/dcmi`：挂载 DCMI 工具用于设备管理。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:117
msgid ""
"`-v /usr/local/bin/npu-smi:/usr/local/bin/npu-smi`: mounts the NPU "
"monitoring command."
msgstr "`-v /usr/local/bin/npu-smi:/usr/local/bin/npu-smi`：挂载 NPU 监控命令。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:118
msgid ""
"`-v /usr/local/Ascend/driver/*`: mounts Ascend driver libraries and "
"version files."
msgstr "`-v /usr/local/Ascend/driver/*`：挂载 Ascend 驱动库和版本文件。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:119
msgid ""
"`-v /etc/ascend_install.info:/etc/ascend_install.info`: mounts Ascend "
"installation metadata."
msgstr "`-v /etc/ascend_install.info:/etc/ascend_install.info`：挂载 Ascend 安装元数据。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2-Thinking.md:120
msgid ""
"`-v /mnt/sfs_turbo/.cache:/home/cache`: mounts the shared model cache "
"directory. Update it if you store model weights elsewhere."
msgstr "`-v /mnt/sfs_turbo/.cache:/home/cache`：挂载共享模型缓存目录。如果模型权重存储在其他位置，请更新此路径。"

